<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Events — Legacy Home &amp; Respite Care Foundation</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:wght@500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>

<div class="demo-banner"><strong>DEMO PREVIEW</strong> · sample data only · built by X-Centric as a working preview for Legacy Home &amp; Respite Care Foundation</div>

<header class="site-header">
  <div class="header-inner">
    <a class="brand" href="index.html">
      <div class="brand-mark">L</div>
      <div class="brand-name">Legacy<small>Home &amp; Respite Care Foundation</small></div>
    </a>
    <button class="nav-toggle" aria-label="Menu" onclick="document.querySelector('.main-nav').classList.toggle('open')">☰</button>
    <nav class="main-nav">
      <a href="index.html">Home</a>
      <a href="about.html">About</a>
      <a href="programs.html">The Sanctuary</a>
      <a href="resources.html">Resource Hub</a>
      <a href="events.html" class="active">Events</a>
      <a href="portal.html" class="nav-portal">Caregiver Portal</a>
      <a href="index.html#donate" class="nav-cta">Donate</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="hero" style="padding: 56px 0 64px;">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 style="font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 44px);">Events</h1>
    <p class="lede">Register in one click — your registration, attendance, and follow-up all connect to your caregiver profile automatically.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card-grid">
{%- for ev in events %}
      <div class="card event-card">
        <div class="event-date"><div class="month">{{ ev.month | e }}</div><div class="day">{{ ev.day | e }}</div></div>
        <div style="flex:1;">
          <span class="badge {{ ev.badge_class }}">{{ ev.badge | e }}</span>
          <h3 style="font-size: 19px; margin: 8px 0 4px;">{{ ev.title | e }}{% if ev.title_badge %} <span class="badge {{ ev.title_badge_class }}">{{ ev.title_badge | e }}</span>{% endif %}</h3>
          <div class="event-meta">{{ ev.meta | e }}</div>
          <p class="small muted mb-8">{{ ev.description | e }}</p>
          <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px;">
            <button class="btn btn-plum btn-sm" onclick="openRegister('{{ ev.register_label | replace("'", "\\'") }}')">Register</button>
            <span class="small muted">{{ ev.registered_note | e }}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
{% endfor %}
    </div>

    <div class="card mt-32" style="background: var(--sand); border-style: dashed;">
      <p class="small" style="margin: 0;"><strong>How staff manage this page:</strong> by chat — <em>"post a Memory Social next Saturday 10–1 in the community room, registration open, capacity 12."</em> The assistant drafts it, staff preview and confirm, and it goes live. Attendance flows back to each caregiver's record for follow-up.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Registration modal -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="registerModal">
  <div class="modal">
    <button class="modal-close" onclick="closeRegister()">✕</button>
    <h3 id="regTitle">Register</h3>
    <p class="sub">One quick form — no re-typing your details every time.</p>
    <form id="regForm" onsubmit="return submitRegister(event)">
      <div class="field">
        <label for="regName">Your name</label>
        <input id="regName" type="text" placeholder="e.g., Maria Gonzalez" required>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="regEmail">Email</label>
        <input id="regEmail" type="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="regRole">I am a…</label>
        <select id="regRole">
          <option>Family caregiver</option>
          <option>Professional caregiver</option>
          <option>Volunteer</option>
          <option>Community member</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-coral" style="width: 100%;">Complete registration</button>
      <div class="success-note" id="regSuccess">✓ You're registered! A confirmation is on its way.</div>
      <div class="routing-note" id="regRouting">Behind the scenes (demo): this registration just routed into the caregiver record — profile matched, attendance list updated, follow-up queued for staff.</div>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>

<footer>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footer-grid">
      <div>
        <h4>Legacy Home &amp; Respite Care Foundation</h4>
        <p style="font-size: 13.5px; max-width: 300px;">A nonprofit supporting caregivers of loved ones with dementia — wellness, respite, and community since 2023.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>The Sanctuary</h4>
        <a href="programs.html#grants">Wellness Grants</a>
        <a href="programs.html#socials">Memory Socials</a>
        <a href="events.html">Support Group &amp; Events</a>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>Get Involved</h4>
        <a href="request-support.html">Request Support</a>
        <a href="#" onclick="alert('Demo: partner/volunteer intake form.'); return false;">Volunteer</a>
        <a href="#" onclick="alert('Demo: organizational partnership form.'); return false;">Partner with us</a>
        <a href="index.html#donate">Donate</a>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>Access</h4>
        <a href="portal.html">Caregiver Portal</a>
        <a href="staff.html">Staff Console (demo)</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <span>© 2026 Legacy Home &amp; Respite Care Foundation · Demo preview — sample data only</span>
      <span>Built &amp; hosted by X-Centric · Managed Hosted Hub</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<script src="app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
